\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Codebreaker.Betty.Allan.Lesson.Plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">End of the Apartheid lesson plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/End.of.Apartheid.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/End.of.Apartheid.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Fall of Communism in Europe/End of Cold War lesson plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Fall.of.Communism.in.Europe.End.of.Cold.War.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Fall.of.Communism.in.Europe.End.of.Cold.War.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Greek Civil War lesson plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Greek.Civil.War.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: 