g: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--cl-anchor-color,#0b8484); text-decoration: var(--cl-anchor-text-decoration,none);\">Create Buyer Personas for Your Business [Free Template]</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.25rem; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; list-style-type: none; position: relative;\"><a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/buyer-persona-research?hubs_content=blog.hubspot.com/marketing/how-to-start-a-blog&hubs_content-cta=Guide%3A%20How%20to%20Create%20Detailed%20Buyer%20Personas%20for%20Your%20Business\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--cl-anchor-color,#0b8484); text-decoration: var(--cl-anchor-text-decoration,none);\">Guide: How to Create Detailed Buyer Personas for Your Business</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.25rem; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: inherit; list-style-type: none; position: relative;\"><a href=\"https://www.hubspot.com/make-my-persona?hubs_post=blog.hubspot.com/marketing/how-to-start-a-blog&hubs_post-cta=%5BFree%20Tool%5D%20Make%20My%20Persona%3A%20Buyer%20Persona%20Generator&hubs_content=blog.hubspot.com/marketing/how-to-start-a-blog&hubs_content-cta=%5BFree%20Tool%5D%20Make%20My%20Persona%3A%20Buyer%20Persona%20Generator\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--cl-anchor-color,#0b8484); text-decoration: var(--cl-anchor-text-decoration,none);\">[Free Tool] Make My Persona: Buyer Persona Generator</a></li></ul><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.5rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 500; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.42; font-family: \"Lexend Deca\", sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(46, 71, 93); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>2. Check out your competition.</h3><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.78; font-family: \"Lexend Deca\", sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(46, 71, 93); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>What better way to draw inspiration than to look at your well-established competition?</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.78; font-family: \"Lexend Deca\", sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(46, 71, 93); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>It&rsquo;s worth taking a look at popular, highly reviewed blogs because their strategy and execution is what got them to grow in credibility. The purpose of doing this isn&rsquo;t to copy these elements, but to gain better insight into what readers appreciate in a quality blog.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1rem 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.78; font-family: \"Lexend Deca\", sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(46, 71, 93); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>When you find a competitor&rsquo;s blog, take the following steps:</p>', 'post-pics/651afd30d01bb_download (2).jpeg', '2023-10-02 17:26:08', NULL);
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `picture`, `created_at`, `category_id`) VALUES
(75, ' Education and Technology:', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" id=\"isPasted\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><br>Education and Technology:</strong></p><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: normal !important; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">Well, education was one. Certainly we looked a lot at high tech, which was very hard for those of us without a high tech background. Many of the folks were really into high tech, but for people like me it was eyes glazing over sometimes. I wish I could have done the year a second time, because with the bit of background that I gained in technology it would have made a lot more sense when we went to Sandia Labs and were talking about artificial intelligence. We looked a lot at grass roots activism in the rural South and we went into the Mississippi Delta area.</p></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 0;\"><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"blob:http://localhost:8000/79149b5b-7fec-4d86-99ea-653c43e61a57\" alt=\"Artificial Intelligence Illustration (2022), David S. Soriano | Wikimedia Commons\" srcset=\"https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/AI-1.webp 512w, https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/AI-1-200x200.webp 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-style: none;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; padding: 0.2em 0.3em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; opacity: 0.7; width: 348px; display: block;\">Artificial Intelligence Illustration (2022), David S. Soriano |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Artificial_General_Intelligence_Illustration.png\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Artificial_General_Intelligence_Illustration.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">Wikimedia Commons</a></figcaption></figure></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Keith Curtis</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Washington, DC&mdash;Deputy Director, Europe Desk, 1995&ndash;1998</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Baghdad, Iraq&mdash;Senior Commercial Officer, 2013&ndash;2014</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&ldquo;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Well, I think there&rsquo;s a lot of BS in the whole AI.&rdquo;</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Are there Bigger Fish than AI?:</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">You didn&rsquo;t really ask about what the future&rsquo;s going to be, but those are changes I would make. I would put them under one roof, and I would pull the plug on the cable system tomorrow. But in terms of where the world&rsquo;s going to go? Who knows. Nobody could predict it if it comes down to the oil or the power market or the cellular market or the social media market. I&rsquo;ve seen enough to be smart enough to not try to predict what&rsquo;s the next big thing. Everybody says AI (artificial intelligence).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Well, I think there&rsquo;s a lot of BS in the whole AI. What I like to think of, is that it&rsquo;s more going to be about how you manage your individual lives. The Bill Gates and the Elon Musks of the world . . . . I do think space has a future. I think aerospace has a real future. I have two boys, and their whole . . . . Not only their professional lives, but their real interest and their real love . . . . You know, they watch all the sci-fi in the world, and these guys want to go back to the moon. They want to go to Mars. They want that in their future, and they work on it. They dream about it and they work on it, and if there were anything they wanted, it would be to reach out and get started. Let&rsquo;s go. So, I do think there&rsquo;s going to be . . . . And that&rsquo;ll be interesting, to see how that develops. Everybody&rsquo;s getting into the space race. But it could be a good thing.</p><hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; overflow: visible; border: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 0px; background-color: var(--colorBorder); min-width: 100px; max-width: 100px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Richard Virden</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Warsaw, Poland&mdash;Information Officer and Press Attach&eacute;, 1977&ndash;1980</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Washington, DC&mdash;The National War College at Ft. McNair, 1983&ndash;1984</p><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.1em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&ldquo;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The cyberwarfare and Artificial Intelligence (AI) experts in our Armed Forces are waging an uphill battle . . . .&rdquo;</em></h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Congressional Conundrum:</strong></p><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: normal !important; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 0;\"><img width=\"512\" height=\"423\" src=\"blob:http://localhost:8000/76afab54-a0ab-4331-90e7-ba16e27bb8ec\" alt=\"The ENIAC Story (n.d.), M. Weik | Wikimedia Commons\" srcset=\"https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/AI-2.webp 512w, https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/AI-2-200x165.webp 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-style: none;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; padding: 0.2em 0.3em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; opacity: 0.7; width: 348px; display: block;\">The ENIAC Story (n.d.), M. Weik |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:ENIAC-changing_a_tube.jpg\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:ENIAC-changing_a_tube.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">Wikimedia Commons</a></figcaption></figure></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">When I was on the faculty of the National War College in the early 2000s, our military experts were beginning to think about how to use social media tools to our benefit and defend against those who would harm us. That task has become even more imperative since the 2016 election.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">The fight, as it so often is, will be about getting resources needed for the job.</p></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">The cyberwarfare and Artificial Intelligence (AI) experts in our Armed Forces are waging an uphill battle for a decent slice of the defense budget.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">They&rsquo;re competing with big ticket hardware like tanks, and planes and ships, which create jobs and so have strong Congressional advocates. The military-industrial-Congressional complex can&rsquo;t just expect more of everything. A choice must be made for the wars of today and tomorrow, not the past. Should we keep building more multi-billion-dollar aircraft carriers&mdash;we already have more of them than the rest of the world combined&mdash;or direct more resources to more modern threats, like cyberwarfare?</p><hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; overflow: visible; border: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 0px; background-color: var(--colorBorder); min-width: 100px; max-width: 100px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Jack Shellenberger</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Washington, DC&mdash;Voice Of America Policy Officer, 1973</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Tokyo, Japan&mdash;Public Affairs Officer, 1984</p><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.1em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&ldquo;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Among the events of the late &rsquo;80s in Japan was the Tsukuba Expo, which was, for the U.S. Pavilion, explaining artificial intelligence.&rdquo;</em></h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">AI in Global Events of the 1980s:</strong></p><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: normal !important; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">The &rsquo;80s&mdash;this is before &rsquo;88&mdash;was also a time of continuing competition and rivalry with the Soviet Union in security matters, and Japan&rsquo;s steadfast performance on the security front and its readiness to share more and more of the burden, the cost of maintaining our forces there I think muted some of the more eager members of the Administration who would mix the political security relationship with that of the trade relationship. Since &rsquo;88 that&rsquo;s changed and I think under the Bush Administration there is disposition to take aim at trading practices that might have not been aimed at with the same force as during the last part of the Reagan Administration. Among the events of the late &rsquo;80s in Japan was the Tsukuba Expo which was, for the U.S. Pavilion explaining artificial intelligence. Complex subject, to say the least. But our involvement was marginal, it was actually managed by an exhibits team of professionals.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 0; display: table;\"><img width=\"342\" height=\"512\" src=\"blob:http://localhost:8000/e2243ced-04f3-4d69-b966-06b52953beed\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/AI-3-1.webp 342w, https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/AI-3-1-200x300.webp 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 342px) 100vw, 342px\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-style: none;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; padding: 0.2em 0.3em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-top: 0.5em; opacity: 0.7; width: 342px; display: table-caption; caption-side: bottom;\">Photo of Codes on Screen (2020), ThisIsEngineering |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/extreme-close-up-photo-of-codes-on-screen-3861976/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.pexels.com/photo/extreme-close-up-photo-of-codes-on-screen-3861976/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">Pexels</a></figcaption></figure></div></div>', 'post-pics/651b111818379_download (2).jpeg', '2023-10-02 18:51:04', NULL),
(76, 'over 100 books by members of the Foreign Service.', '<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 2em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;\" id=\"isPasted\">Our Popular Products and Projects</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; The ADST.org&nbsp;</span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">website attracts over one million visits annually</b><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&ndash; everyone from journalists to practicing diplomats, distinguished academics and students from around the world.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; Our web series of&nbsp;</span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">800&nbsp;</b><a href=\"https://adst.org/moments\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">&ldquo;Moments in Diplomatic History&rdquo;</b></a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;captures key historical events &ndash; and humorous aspects of diplomatic life.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; Our&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://adst.org/oral-history\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">oral histories cover almost eight decades</b></a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">, including histories of pioneering African-American, Hispanic, and Women diplomats. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; Our&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://adst.org/podcasts/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">70+ podcasts</b></a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;are available through iTunes, Spotify, and Google Podcasts.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; ADST has facilitated the publication of&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://adst.org/publications\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">over 100 books by members of the Foreign Service.</b></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; We are committed to&nbsp;</span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">educational outreach</b><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">. ADST&rsquo;s website has sample lesson plans for high schools and universities on a broad range of topics. We also work closely with local and national partners to strengthen the understanding of and support for diplomacy in the education system.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">&ndash; We support the work of the&nbsp;</span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">State Department&rsquo;s Foreign Service Institute</b><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400;\">, providing critical source material for those who are training today&rsquo;s diplomats &ndash; and tomorrow&rsquo;s.</span></p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.3em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Video Snapshot</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px !important; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rYvTJngW1Eg\" width=\"550\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" align=\"center\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px 1em 1em 0px;\"></iframe></p><p><br></p>', 'post-pics/651b11ea37517_images.jpeg', '2023-10-02 18:54:34', NULL),
(77, 'Stand-alone Lesson Plans', '<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: normal !important; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" id=\"isPasted\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); line-height: 1.36; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 200; font-size: calc(1em + 1.5vmin); font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; text-align: left; font-style: normal;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Lesson Plans and Unit Studies</strong></strong></h2><hr style=\"box-sizing: content-box; overflow: visible; border: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; background-color: var(--colorBorder); clear: both; text-align: center; min-width: 100px; max-width: none !important;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; height: 50px;\"><br></div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: normal !important; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 1.5em;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 0; min-width: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 33.33%;\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; line-height: 0;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/intern-teacher-pic-2-830x1024.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-style: none;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><img src=\"blob:http://localhost:8000/7212e3eb-597c-4bd0-91e3-07a1868a9a7c\" style=\"width: 300px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/citations-book-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br id=\"isPasted\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://adst.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/citations-book-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; border-style: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></figure></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 0; min-width: 40px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 66.66%;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.3em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">The Red Scare Unit Study (ADST/Cox Foundation)</strong></strong></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">The First Red Scare Lesson Plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.First.Red.Scare.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.First.Red.Scare.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Second Red Scare Lesson Plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Second.Red.Scare.and.McCarthyism.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Second.Red.Scare.and.McCarthyism.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Lavender Scare Lesson Plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Lavender.Scare.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Lavender.Scare.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.3em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Stand-alone Lesson Plans</strong></strong></strong></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">Black Diplomats Break Barriers Lesson Plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Black.Diplomats.Break.Barriers.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Black.Diplomats.Break.Barriers.lesson.plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Codebreaker Betty Allan Lesson Plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Codebreaker.Betty.Allan.Lesson.Plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Codebreaker.Betty.Allan.Lesson.Plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">End of the Apartheid lesson plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/End.of.Apartheid.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/End.of.Apartheid.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Fall of Communism in Europe/End of Cold War lesson plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Fall.of.Communism.in.Europe.End.of.Cold.War.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Fall.of.Communism.in.Europe.End.of.Cold.War.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Greek Civil War lesson plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Greek.Civil.War.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Greek.Civil.War.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Suez Canal Lesson Plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Suez.Canal.Lesson.Plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Suez.Canal.Lesson.Plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tet Offensive Lesson Plan (ADST/USDC) (<a href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Tet.Offensive.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Tet.Offensive.lesson.plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\"><br></p></div></div></div></div>', 'post-pics/651b12d6ba53a_images.png', '2023-10-02 18:58:30', NULL);
