(78, 'Use the box below to search oral history transcripts.', '<div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: normal !important; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" id=\"isPasted\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; flex-grow: 1; min-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; margin-left: 0px !important; flex-basis: 0px;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" id=\"isPasted\"><section style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; max-width: 1140px; margin: auto; padding-top: 3em; padding-bottom: 1em;\"><h1 itemprop=\"headline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 2em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif;\">Oral Histories: Search Our Collection</h1></div></section></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; flex-grow: 1; overflow: hidden;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; max-width: 1140px; margin: auto; padding-bottom: 5em;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><main style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><article style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><div itemprop=\"text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; counter-reset: footnotes 0;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.5em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Welcome!&nbsp;It&rsquo;s easy to search our collection:</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JdB8qA7gPmY\" width=\"486\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"3\" align=\"center\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px 1em;\"></iframe></p><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.1em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">For an Advanced Search of transcripts of over 2600 oral histories, see below.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">For tips on how to combine search terms click&nbsp;<a href=\"https://adst.org/boolean-searches\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">here.</a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><br></p></h5><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: var(--colorDarkMuted); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.1em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Advanced Search: Use the box below to search oral history transcripts.</h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.32px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Please cite this material as follows: &nbsp;INTERVIEWEE FULL NAME Oral History, Interviewed by INTERVIEWER FULL NAME, Foreign Affairs Oral History Collection, Association for Diplomatic Studies and Training, Arlington, VA, adst.org.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 