gb(0, 51, 102); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.3em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">The Red Scare Unit Study (ADST/Cox Foundation)</strong></strong></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">The First Red Scare Lesson Plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.First.Red.Scare.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.First.Red.Scare.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Second Red Scare Lesson Plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Second.Red.Scare.and.McCarthyism.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Second.Red.Scare.and.McCarthyism.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Lavender Scare Lesson Plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Lavender.Scare.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Lavender.Scare.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 51, 102); line-height: 1.34; margin-top: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1.3em; font-family: Merriweather, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Stand-alone Lesson Plans</strong></strong></strong></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5em !important;\">Black Diplomats Break Barriers Lesson Plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Black.Diplomats.Break.Barriers.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Black.Diplomats.Break.Barriers.lesson.plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Codebreaker Betty Allan Lesson Plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Codebreaker.Betty.Allan.Lesson.Plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Codebreaker.Betty.Allan.Lesson.Plan.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">End of the Apartheid lesson plan (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/End.of.Apartheid.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/End.of.Apartheid.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.docx\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Fall of Communism in Europe/End of Cold War lesson plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Fall.of.Communism.in.Europe.End.of.Cold.War.lesson.plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">pdf</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/Fall.of.Communism.in.Europe.End.of.Cold.War.lesson.plan.doc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: var(--colorMain3);\">doc</a>)<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Greek Civil War lesson plan (ADST/Cox Foundation) (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.adst.org/OH%20TOCs/The.Greek.Civil.War.lesson.plan.grades.9-12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: 